title: Big Thicket National Preserve: Plants
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Nature     Plants               Plants       The array of different hydrologic, slope, drainage, and soil features result in the very different plant community assemblages described below. This in turn adds to the wonderful complexity of terrestrial and aquatic vascular plants, mosses, lichens, fungi, molds, etc. that call Big Thicket home.
